description:
the function /nova/virt/libvirt/volume.py  def _delete_mpath(self, iscsi_properties, multipath_device, ips_iqns):   the multipath_device parameter has  been not  used .so the parameter "multipath_device" no need. we should remove the parameter "multipath_device".

This problem also exists in the K version.
title: The function _delete_mpath has no valid parameter
